<p local-id=3D"2e67fb727032">EC2 + EBS + R53 Zone</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"3001d641376f"><strong>~$10.67/month</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b666fb0bc731">Ongoing EC2 cost + operational overhead</p></t=
d>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b0f348698bfb"><strong>Route 53 Only Total</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0e05214e757b">Hosted Zone + Queries</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"617f97213582"><strong>~$0.90/month</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2b5082e89063">No EC2; fully managed; no ops overhead</p></td=
>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"b78b4bc512b6"><strong>Cost Optimisation Recommendations:</st=
rong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"3a99118759af"><strong>Use Route 53 for Production DNS:</stro=
ng> At $0.90/month vs $10.67/month, Route 53 is approximately 12x more cost=
-effective and eliminates all infrastructure management overhead for DNS</p=
></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"395a939ccdde"><strong>Decommission BIND9 EC2 Post-Evaluation=
:</strong> The EC2 BIND9 server serves its purpose as a learning and evalua=
tion environment; it should be terminated after the evaluation is complete =
to stop accumulating EC2 and EBS charges</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"7dc6bc2051a2"><strong>Reserved Instance if Retained:</strong=
> If the BIND9 EC2 is kept long-term for internal DNS or hybrid use cases, =
converting to a 1-year Reserved Instance reduces the EC2 cost from $8.47 to=
 approximately $5.10/month =E2=80=94 a 40% saving</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"d89e67d0ebf7"><strong>Route 53 Resolver for Internal DNS:</s=
trong> For internal AWS VPC DNS resolution, AWS Route 53 Resolver is includ=
ed at no additional charge =E2=80=94 eliminating the need for a BIND9 EC2 f=
or internal name resolution entirely</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"ceb13e05ad01"><strong>Business Value Analysis:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"966a13aeb95c"><strong>Operational Cost Saving:</strong> Rout=
e 53 eliminates BIND9 patching, service monitoring, and incident response o=
verhead =E2=80=94 estimated saving of 2=E2=80=934 DevOps hours per month, a=
t a typical rate of $50=E2=80=93$100/hour this is $100=E2=80=93$400/month i=
n operational cost avoided</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"52ab182be646"><strong>Reliability Improvement:</strong> Rout=
e 53 provides a 100% uptime SLA backed by AWS's global Anycast infrastructu=
re; a single EC2 BIND9 instance has no SLA and is a single point of failure=
 =E2=80=94 one EC2 stop event causes complete DNS outage for the zone</p></=
li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"34fca74e39df"><strong>DNS Propagation Speed:</strong> Route =
53 propagates record changes globally within 60 seconds; BIND9 changes are =
limited by TTL values and manual serial number management</p></li>
<li>
<p local-id=3D"561bacc26113"><strong>Learning ROI:</strong> The BIND9 hands=
-on exercise builds deep DNS knowledge (SOA records, zone files, NS delegat=
ion, glue records, dig tracing) that directly improves the team's ability t=
o configure, troubleshoot, and optimise Route 53 in production environments=
</p></li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h1 local-id=3D"2ca15c05b89c" id=3D"Task20-Technicaldocument-9.Step-by-Step=
Implementation">9. Step-by-Step Implementation</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"a208971fce68" id=3D"Task20-Technicaldocument-Step1:InstallB=
IND9">Step 1: Install BIND9</h2>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">sudo ap=
t update
sudo apt install bind9 -y</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h2 local-id=3D"647541c1983b" id=3D"Task20-Technicaldocument-Step3:Configur=
eBIND9">Step 3: Configure BIND9</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"b53e9917a4ab" id=3D"Task20-Technicaldocument-Openconfigfile=
:">Open config file:</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">sudo na=
no /etc/bind/named.conf.local</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h2 local-id=3D"01bf81b77b59" id=3D"Task20-Technicaldocument-Step5:CreateZo=
neFile">Step 5: Create Zone File</h2>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">sudo cp=
 /etc/bind/db.local /etc/bind/db.lab.karna.pushkar.cloud
sudo nano /etc/bind/db.lab.karna.pushkar.cloud</pre>
</div>
